metadata.name: Bella Ballerina Puppy Love 1
metadata.description:
This collection was taken just over a year ago when my dog Vienna was just a puppy. How ever cute and serene she may look i can assure you this shoot was more difficult than it looks.

With the purchase of this NFT you also get a printed signed version if you wish, the chance to be my Patreon and met ups with me if you so wish. You can contact me to organise once purchased via any of my platforms.

https://linktr.ee/bellaballerina
